Name: Tamiku
About the game: In a distant galaxy there is an alien totally obsessed with blow up balloons. Having extinguished all that is on your planet now you have to travel to other worlds to look for more. Tamiku is an action and platform game in which you have to burst all the balloons of a level without being killed. To do this you will face different dangers, jump, run and quickly inflate the red balloons!
